WEBVTT

00:03.900 --> 00:05.510
Ariel, what's going on in there?

00:05.560 --> 00:06.870
Did you fall in or something?

00:09.170 --> 00:09.990
Seriously!

00:10.040 --> 00:11.660
You're going to make
us late for school!

00:12.530 --> 00:13.950
ARIEL : I told you, go away.

00:14.580 --> 00:15.800
Hey, hey. Take it easy.

00:16.290 --> 00:18.280
25. Why aren't you guys dressed?

00:18.530 --> 00:19.300
We would be...

00:19.330 --> 00:21.860
If Ariel would get
out of the bathroom!

00:22.220 --> 00:25.220
She's been in there for, like,
20 minutes. Okay, okay.

00:25.310 --> 00:26.910
Ariel, you all right in there?

00:27.570 --> 00:29.280
Just go away, Dad.

00:29.930 --> 00:31.630
Just go... go use me
and Mom's bathroom.

00:31.660 --> 00:33.409
But my toothbrush
is in this bathroom.

00:33.410 --> 00:34.449
All right, just your finger.

00:34.450 --> 00:35.330
Go on, go on.

00:35.930 --> 00:36.740
Ariel.

00:37.550 --> 00:39.810
Whatever it is,
we'll figure it out, okay?

00:39.940 --> 00:42.490
No! You can't figure this out.

00:43.290 --> 00:44.760
You want me to go get Mom?

00:44.930 --> 00:45.760
No!

00:45.880 --> 00:47.690
Mom can't help me. No one can.

00:47.730 --> 00:49.110
Ariel, come on, now!

00:50.230 --> 00:51.830
All right, open the door.
I'm serious.

00:51.870 --> 00:52.940
You want me to go get the key?

01:00.710 --> 01:01.570
Ariel?

01:04.080 --> 01:05.150
Help me, Daddy.

01:06.960 --> 01:08.940
What's wrong with me, Daddy?

01:10.350 --> 01:12.190
What's happening to me?

01:19.760 --> 01:20.930
Oh, no.

01:22.810 --> 01:25.230
Ariel, honey,
what are you doing up?

01:26.850 --> 01:28.740
58 in the morning.

01:28.790 --> 01:31.590
You promised me you weren't
going to study past 12:00.

01:32.660 --> 01:35.410
Uh, I... I wasn't planning to.

01:35.540 --> 01:37.629
I just took a practice quiz

01:37.630 --> 01:39.660
and realized I had a lot
more studying to do.

01:40.810 --> 01:41.880
What are you doing up?

01:43.280 --> 01:44.420
Weird dream.

01:44.910 --> 01:46.910
Thought I'd get a glass of milk.
Do you want one?

01:47.020 --> 01:49.360
Mom, I'm trying to stay awake.

01:50.530 --> 01:52.290
Honey, come on.

01:52.340 --> 01:54.580
You know I don't like you
pulling these all-nighters.

01:54.630 --> 01:55.920
You're not going to
learn anything new

01:55.921 --> 01:58.080
58 in the morning. I know.

01:58.450 --> 01:59.580
I know. I just...

01:59.750 --> 02:01.420
I need, like, ten more minutes.

02:03.520 --> 02:06.480
And that glass of milk
sounds really nice, actually.

